---
title: Grilled Old Bay Shrimp Skewers with Potato Wedges and Dill-Garlic Lemon Sauce
description: Skewers are perfect for grilling bite-sized food like shrimp! This irresistible dill-garlic lemon sauce is great smothered on shrimp, wedges and veggies alike!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/brochettes-de-crevettes-grillees-aux-epices-old-bay-b8c7c5e0.jpg
